dsl Picota

Reality Infecar
	ViewPoint weather
		Variable temperature as Numeric
		Variable radiation as Numeric
	Entity SolarPlant
		ViewPoint operational
			Variable cellTemperature as Numeric
		ViewPoint generation
			Variable reactivePower as Numeric
			Variable activePower as Numeric
		ViewPoint consumption
			Variable reactivePower as Numeric
			Variable activePower as Numeric

DigitalTwin(Infecar.SolarPlant) predictiveEnergyGeneration as Predictive(timeHorizon = 6, lag = 0)
	Resolution(5, Minute)
	Infer(Infecar.SolarPlant.generation.activePower)
	Infer(Infecar.SolarPlant.generation.reactivePower)